#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:4
msgid "重设几何形状"
msgstr "Reshape Geometry"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:6
msgid "有时候我们会遇到这样的情景：想要根据几何参数重新设置图形的尺寸或轮廓，我们也许会这么做："
msgstr ""
"Sometimes we encounter this situation: we want to reset a shape's size or contour based on geometric parameters, and we "
"might do this:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:8
msgid ""
"# 第一次创建\n"
"circle = Circle(radius=2)\n"
"\n"
"...\n"
"\n"
"# ? 重设几何参数\n"
"circle.become(Circle(radius=1.2))"
msgstr ""
"# First creation\n"
"circle = Circle(radius=2)\n"
"\n"
"...\n"
"\n"
"# ? Reset geometric parameters\n"
"circle.become(Circle(radius=1.2))"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:18
msgid "虽然这种方法能够达到目的，但是这种重新创建物件的方式存在两大问题："
msgstr "Although this method works, recreating items this way has two major problems:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:20
msgid ""
"我们需要临时创建一个 :class:`~.Circle`，把它的数据“偷”过来，然后马上把它给抛弃掉，显得比较麻烦；并且这在频繁调用时会略微拖"
"累性能"
msgstr ""
"We need to temporarily create a :class:`~.Circle`, \"borrow\" its data, and then discard it immediately, which is "
"cumbersome; and when called frequently, it can slightly hurt performance"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:21
msgid "临时创建的 :class:`~.Circle` 无法跟随当前物件的位置，导致需要更多麻烦的操作来对齐位置"
msgstr ""
"The temporarily created :class:`~.Circle` cannot follow the current item's position, so extra cumbersome operations are "
"needed for alignment"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:23
msgid ""
"当你希望“还是同一个物件，只是换一个尺寸或轮廓”时，几何物件提供了 :meth:`~.GeometryShape.reshape` 方法来帮助你做到这一点。"
msgstr ""
"When you want \"the same item, just with a different size or contour\", geometry items "
"provide :meth:`~.GeometryShape.reshape` to help you do this."

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:26
msgid "``reshape`` 适合的场景"
msgstr "When ``reshape`` Fits"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:28
msgid ":meth:`~.GeometryShape.reshape` 适合“参数化改形状”的需求，例如："
msgstr ":meth:`~.GeometryShape.reshape` is suitable for \"parameterized shape changes\", for example:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:30
msgid "改圆的半径"
msgstr "Change a circle's radius"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:31
msgid "改矩形的宽高"
msgstr "Change a rectangle's width and height"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:32
msgid "改圆角矩形的圆角大小"
msgstr "Change a rounded rectangle's corner radius"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:34
msgid "相比临时构造一个物件，:meth:`~.GeometryShape.reshape` 的优势是："
msgstr "Compared with temporarily constructing a new item, :meth:`~.GeometryShape.reshape` has these advantages:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:36
msgid "代码更简洁，直接传入新的参数即可，无需临时创建一个新物件"
msgstr "The code is simpler: just pass new parameters directly, without creating a temporary item"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:37
msgid ""
"可以缺省参数，例如只改圆角矩形的圆角大小，保持宽高不变；需要另外注意的是，缺省的参数会根据原先传递给构造函数的值来决定，而"
"不是物件当前状态的宽高"
msgstr ""
"Parameters can be omitted, for example changing only a rounded rectangle's corner radius while keeping width and height "
"unchanged; note that omitted parameters are determined by values originally passed to the constructor, not by the item's "
"current width and height"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:38
msgid "对于一些几何物件，可以保持当前物件的位置不变，无需额外对齐操作"
msgstr "For some geometry items, the current position can be kept unchanged, with no extra alignment operations"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:41
msgid "使用方式"
msgstr "Usage"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:43
msgid "你可以把它理解为“用新的形状参数，重新描述当前物件”，可以重新设置一些原先传给构造函数的参数："
msgstr ""
"You can understand it as \"re-describing the current item with new shape parameters\"; you can reset some parameters "
"originally passed to the constructor:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:45
msgid "item.reshape(...)"
msgstr "item.reshape(...)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:49
msgid "在动画中，常见写法是："
msgstr "In animations, a common form is:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:51
msgid "self.play(item.anim.reshape(...))"
msgstr "self.play(item.anim.reshape(...))"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:55
msgid "下面用两个常见图形演示 :meth:`~.GeometryShape.reshape` 的用法。"
msgstr "Below we demonstrate :meth:`~.GeometryShape.reshape` with two common shapes."

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:13
msgid ""
"circle = Circle(radius=0.8, color=BLUE, fill_alpha=0.4).show()\n"
"\n"
"self.forward()\n"
"self.play(circle.anim.reshape(1.8))\n"
"self.forward(0.5)\n"
"self.play(circle.anim.reshape(0.5))\n"
"self.forward()\n"
"\n"
"circle.hide()\n"
"\n"
"rect = RoundedRect(3.6, 1.6, corner_radius=0.25, color=TEAL, fill_alpha=0.35).show()\n"
"\n"
"self.forward()\n"
"self.play(rect.anim.reshape(5.2, 2.4, corner_radius=0.5))\n"
"self.forward(0.5)\n"
"self.play(rect.anim.reshape(corner_radius=0.15))\n"
"self.forward(0.5)\n"
"self.play(rect.anim.reshape(UL, DR))\n"
"self.forward()"
msgstr ""
"circle = Circle(radius=0.8, color=BLUE, fill_alpha=0.4).show()\n"
"\n"
"self.forward()\n"
"self.play(circle.anim.reshape(1.8))\n"
"self.forward(0.5)\n"
"self.play(circle.anim.reshape(0.5))\n"
"self.forward()\n"
"\n"
"circle.hide()\n"
"\n"
"rect = RoundedRect(3.6, 1.6, corner_radius=0.25, color=TEAL, fill_alpha=0.35).show()\n"
"\n"
"self.forward()\n"
"self.play(rect.anim.reshape(5.2, 2.4, corner_radius=0.5))\n"
"self.forward(0.5)\n"
"self.play(rect.anim.reshape(corner_radius=0.15))\n"
"self.forward(0.5)\n"
"self.play(rect.anim.reshape(UL, DR))\n"
"self.forward()"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:81
msgid "一个更复杂的例子："
msgstr "A more complex example:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/geometry_reshape.rst:13
msgid ""
"path = VItem(\n"
"    [-6.2, 0.76, 0], [-4.45, 0.65, 0], [-3.43, 0.14, 0], [-2.95, -0.11, 0], [-1.89, -0.82, 0],\n"
"    [-0.64, -1.66, 0], [0.03, -2, 0], [1.3, -2.64, 0], [4.07, -3.28, 0],\n"
"    color=[BLUE, RED]\n"
").show()\n"
"\n"
"star = Star(start_angle=10 * DEGREES, color=YELLOW, fill_alpha=0.5).show()\n"
"star.points.to_border(UR, buff=0.75)\n"
"\n"
"dot = Dot()\n"
"\n"
"arrow = Arrow(color=YELLOW, alpha=[0, 1])\n"
"\n"
"self.play(\n"
"    MoveAlongPath(dot, path),\n"
"    DataUpdater(\n"
"        dot,\n"
"        lambda data, p:\n"
"            data.reshape(radius=DEFAULT_DOT_RADIUS * (1 + 3 * p.alpha))\n"
"                .glow.set(alpha=p.alpha)\n"
"    ),\n"
"    GroupUpdater(\n"
"        arrow,\n"
"        lambda group, p: group.reshape(dot.current(), star)\n"
"    ),\n"
"    duration=4\n"
")"
msgstr ""
"path = VItem(\n"
"    [-6.2, 0.76, 0], [-4.45, 0.65, 0], [-3.43, 0.14, 0], [-2.95, -0.11, 0], [-1.89, -0.82, 0],\n"
"    [-0.64, -1.66, 0], [0.03, -2, 0], [1.3, -2.64, 0], [4.07, -3.28, 0],\n"
"    color=[BLUE, RED]\n"
").show()\n"
"\n"
"star = Star(start_angle=10 * DEGREES, color=YELLOW, fill_alpha=0.5).show()\n"
"star.points.to_border(UR, buff=0.75)\n"
"\n"
"dot = Dot()\n"
"\n"
"arrow = Arrow(color=YELLOW, alpha=[0, 1])\n"
"\n"
"self.play(\n"
"    MoveAlongPath(dot, path),\n"
"    DataUpdater(\n"
"        dot,\n"
"        lambda data, p:\n"
"            data.reshape(radius=DEFAULT_DOT_RADIUS * (1 + 3 * p.alpha))\n"
"                .glow.set(alpha=p.alpha)\n"
"    ),\n"
"    GroupUpdater(\n"
"        arrow,\n"
"        lambda group, p: group.reshape(dot.current(), star)\n"
"    ),\n"
"    duration=4\n"
")"

